{"tid":906183,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇視光師or body check 姑娘，色弱問題想問","createTime":"2018-11-17T17:49:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-19T14:04:20.000Z","uid":113823,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"619245dccb97913397480e16c70138aa76a178a4","tid":906183,"uid":113823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T17:49:11.000Z","msg":"話說早幾日去左做body check，唔知係咪太緊張，有幾個波波圖睇唔到，最後要排d15<br />\n<br />\n排左兩次d15，第一次唔知點排，但我肯定錯左，因為冇出漸變色<br />\n<br />\n第二次就有漸變色，由藍到紫。<br />\n<br />\n最後姑娘冇同我講有冇問題，佢話會直接pass比公司知。<br />\n<br />\n搞到好唔安樂，想問D15 係計最好果次定係兩次都會睇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ead363baddd84bcc2eee2328f56fc55eb6191df3","tid":906183,"uid":30351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T18:03:21.000Z","msg":"咪傻啦，如果一個test會因為你狀態唔好而得出唔同結果，咁即係呢個test好有問題。色弱啲波點圖沿用左咁多年，應該唔存在呢個問題。<br />\n<br />\n應該係你本身色弱"},{"pid":"acf1c60475e44dbe0e858359847e87bac80ce72a","tid":906183,"uid":113823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ead363baddd84bcc2eee2328f56fc55eb6191df3","tid":906183,"uid":30351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T18:03:21.000Z","msg":"咪傻啦，如果一個test會因為你狀態唔好而得出唔同結果，咁即係呢個test好有問題。色弱啲波點圖沿用左咁多年，應該唔存在呢個問題。<br />\n<br />\n應該係你本身色弱"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T18:08:20.000Z","msg":"唔該晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我想知d15 排兩次係咪睇最好果次？"},{"pid":"39f52d22ab50137bb86d8b782dd9c1525c2238e9","tid":906183,"uid":113823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T02:23:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"50de864c33a5a19c96d9caf2a5a82cd2128afc02","tid":906183,"uid":113823,"l